.TH WLA\-SUPERFX 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-superfx \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the Nintendo SuperFX coprocessor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-superfx
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-superfx
assembles Nintendo SuperFX source code to a WLA DX object file.
The SuperFX (GSU-1/GSU-2) is a RISC coprocessor used in SNES cartridges
such as Star Fox, Stunt Race FX, Yoshi's Island, and Doom.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wla\-65816 (1),
.BR wla\-cx4 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
